<SYNC Start=5766390><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5768670><P Class=KRCC>
엄호해
<SYNC Start=5770001><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=5770705><P Class=KRCC>
